- **`R/viz_deconvolution.R`** (new): method × method correlation heatmap, per-method agreement distribution boxplot, method × cell-type mean-composition heatmap, per-cell-type agreement heatmap (which cell types drive each method's agreement), cross-method spread per cell type (flags method-sensitive vs. method-robust cell types), per-method distance-from-baseline bar, method clustering dendrogram, and per-cell-type method-vs-baseline scatter grid.
